    <p>Put your skills and experience into action and join Canada World Youth and Youth Challenge International as a volunteer on our innovative youth development project, EQWIP HUBs.</p>
    <p>Located in six countries around the world, EQWIP HUBs are dynamic learning spaces where local young women and men benefit from employment and entrepreneurship training and youth-to-youth mentorship, and find the support they need to help propel themselves, their communities, and the world, forward.</p>
